javazaawansowana.lab1

Class BruteForceAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • javazaawansowana.lab1.BruteForceAlgorithm
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AlgorithmInterface

    public class BruteForceAlgorithm
extends java.lang.Object
implements AlgorithmInterface
    Class designed to solve Knapsack Problem with brute force algorithm. It solves all possible solutions that is equal to 2 to power of size of list of items. Works for small amount of items. For big amount of items it may last an eternity to find the best solution.
    Author:
    Kamil Kluba 226016
    See Also:
    KnapsackProblem, Knapsack, Item, GreedyAlgorithm, RandomAlgorithm
